Rommo RAGLAND . J OHANNE FLEMYNG . J OHANNE ap J EVAN ap Tuoms . Tuom FLEMYNG . J OHANNE de AUNE . et multis aliis.

Datum apud LESWRONNY sexto die Novembris anno regni Regis EDWARDI

quarti post conquestum quinto. Endorsed-‘ Roberte Velle.’

The seventeenth century copy of this deed, from which the above is taken (original being lost), is in- correct in places. The enumeration 01⁸ the acreage appears only to account for 80ss instead of 81 acres.

Lisworney appears to be spelt in several ways. Leswronny looks most like the present name, but Leswrunny appears.
